# GemHub Lite — environment template
#
# GemHub Lite is intentionally offline-first and self-contained: all data
# (products + media) lives in on-device SQLite and the app's file storage.
# There are NO required secrets, API keys, or backend endpoints.
#
# This file exists so the repo has zero hard-coded secrets and a documented,
# copy-to-`.env` starting point. Copy it if you add optional configuration:
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# No variables are required to build or run the app. Add your own here only
# if you introduce optional configuration later.
